---

<div id="container" class="min-h-screen w-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="title mb-16">FAQ</h2>
    <div class="faq-timeline">
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: left;">
                <h3>What is 512?</h3>
                <p>512 is a Hack Club YSWS where you ship a optimized website, and we ship you retro prizes, including old consoles, tech, and more. And stickers. Stickers for everyone.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-end;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: right;">
                <h3>How do I check?</h3>
                <p>
                    Use <a href="https://radar.cloudflare.com/scan" class="underline">Cloudflare Radar</a> to scan your website and see its size.
                    (P.S: This site is under 512KB!)
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: left;">
                <h3>What is the 512KB Club?</h3>
                <p>Check out <a href="https://512kb.club/" class="underline">512kb.club</a> to learn more about the club and its mission.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-end;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: right;">
                <h3>What is Hack Club?</h3>
                <p>Hack Club is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization based in the U.S. aimed at supporting teenagers develop their skills. We have organized events such as High Seas and Shipwrecked in the past. You can see more of what we do at <a href="https://hackclub.com" class="underline">hackclub.com</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: left;">
                <h3>Who can participate?</h3>
                <p>Anyone between ages 13-18 can participate no matter their skill level!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-end;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: right;">
                <h3>I have more questions!</h3>
                <p>Join Hack Club's Slack and join #512 to connect with the community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-start;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: left;">
                <h3>Who made this?</h3>
                <p>@hna &lt;3</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-row" style="justify-content: flex-end;">
            <div class="faq-content" style="max-width: 45%; text-align: right;">
                <h3>How do I earn a console?</h3>
                <p>Make an amazing project, and your site can be chosen to receive a retro gaming console :D</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .title {
        font-family: 'Jacquard 12', serif;
        font-size: 8vw;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .faq-timeline {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        padding: 0 60px;
    }
    
    .faq-row {
        display: flex;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        width: 100%;
    }
    
    .faq-content {
        background: transparent;
        border-radius: 0;
        padding: 40px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        image-rendering: pixelated;
    }
    
    .faq-content:hover {
        background: transparent;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    
    .faq-content h3 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .faq-content p {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin: 0;
        color: inherit;
    }
    

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .faq-timeline {
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .faq-row {
            justify-content: center !important;
        }
        
        .faq-content {
            max-width: 90% !important;
        }
        

    }
</style>